 Magnus looked at himself. He couldnt believe it had come to this. he felt 
Galvatron fastly approaching. What could he do. He knew that optimus was more 
then a match for Galvatron right now. But Optimus would never make it in 
thime. He was on his own. This was his last shot for peace. He opened his 
chest and exposed his matrix. The matrix of peace. It was his last hope to 
defeat Galvatron. He flew out of the base with insane speed. 

--part1_92.faf86c2.27a8bea8_boundary
